                'usage_guidance' => "This metric is intended to capture the percentage of company shares that are owned by women.\n\nWhere regional or local laws apply for calculating ownership by previously excluded groups (including women), reporting should be consistent with these laws. Where laws do not exist, shares that are publicly traded or owned by institutions cannot contribute to the number of female-owned shares.",
