                'usage_guidance' => "This metric is intended to capture a detailed description of the product or service provided from among the options given in the definition. \n\nOrganizations can report on this metric at an organizational level (selecting all product/service details that apply) or for a specific product/service (selecting the product/service detail for which the organization is reporting).\n\nOrganizations providing water, sanitation, and hygiene (WASH) services may use this metric in conjunction with WASH Facilities Type (PD3668) to more specifically describe the facilities provided to target stakeholders through their investments.",
